---
import Layout from '../../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="WKDevKitApp Privacy Policy"
	description="Privacy Policy for WKDevKitApp"
	pubDate={new Date('January 26 2026')}
>
	<h2>Privacy Policy for WKDevKitApp</h2>
	<p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 26, 2026</p>

	<h3>Introduction</h3>
	<p>
		WKDevKitApp ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy
		explains how we handle information when you use our application.
	</p>

	<h3>Information We Collect</h3>
	<p>
		<strong>WKDevKitApp does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.</strong>
	</p>
	<p>
		Our app is designed as a development toolkit that operates entirely on your device. We do not:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Collect personal information</li>
		<li>Track your location</li>
		<li>Access your contacts, photos, or other device data</li>
		<li>Use analytics or tracking services</li>
		<li>Store any data on external servers</li>
	</ul>

	<h3>Data Storage</h3>
	<p>
		Any data you create or configure within the app is stored locally on your device. This data
		remains under your control and is not accessible to us or any third parties.
	</p>

	<h3>Third-Party Services</h3>
	<p>
		WKDevKitApp does not integrate with any third-party services that collect user data.
	</p>

	<h3>Children's Privacy</h3>
	<p>
		Our app does not collect any personal information from anyone, including children under 13
		years of age.
	</p>

	<h3>Changes to This Policy</h3>
	<p>
		We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this
		page with an updated "Last Updated" date.
	</p>

	<h3>Contact Us</h3>
	<p>
		If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
	</p>
	<p>
		<a href="mailto:evan@mightystrong.io">evan@mightystrong.io</a>
	</p>
</Layout>
